{
  "stem": "443.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the only way we survived, again, is we were eating snow all the way through, till we wind up again in Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] It just looked like they didn't know what to do with the people anymore, so they brought us back to Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "When we arrived in Bergen-Belsen, those people that we left a few weeks before, they were all in the streets, scattered around, dead.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Some of them were in such a bad condition you couldn't touch them anymore.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You had to put them on-- on a wagon to be able to move them, because they felt apart.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You touched a limb, you touched an arm, it just came off, because there's nothing to hold it together.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But those that they could be moved, we would put four people to each person.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we had a belt.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So we used to tie a belt to a body, because we were so weak.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You couldn't do it by yourself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You had to have four people to do it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Besides, a dead body's heavier than a-- a person that's alive.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we had to drag the person into the barracks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We had special barracks where they threw one dead body after another, one on top of the other.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Just like you take wood.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "You pile wood one on top of the other, that's how we piled these, all dead bodies.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "After doing this for a few days, and I just kept on seeing this.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "There's no end.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Nobody's going to come out of this alive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We were nothing but skeletons.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We had just about enough energy to be able to make a step.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Besides, we have to work yet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We had to pull these dead people.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
